<node CREATED="1189109168906" ID="Freemind_Link_1993471504" MODIFIED="1189109249078" TEXT="In this tutorial, we create a 3D version of Blender&apos;s 2D logo. When we&apos;re done, we&apos;ll have a very accurate model of our favorite 3D application&apos;s logo.&#xa;&#xa;What&apos;s covered:&#xa;&#xa;    * Adding a background image (or blueprint)&#xa;    * Using curves for modeling iconic images and lettering&#xa;    * and more&#xa;&#xa;http://www.blendernewbies.com/tutorials/swf/model_blender_logo/bn_model_blender_logo.zip&#xa;Download the 52.6MB ZIP file to view it offline (load the HTML file in your browser)."/>
