<node CREATED="1189420584562" MODIFIED="1189420584562" TEXT="I want to say that part of the reason this image looks a little funny on the right edge is due to lens distortion. The original image was rendered with a 16 mm lens and the cloud was only in the upper right corner. Instead of rerendering it in the center, I just cropped it. Take a look at the other images on the blenderartists post, and if you have better ideas, give them up, or if you&apos;ve seen better clouds in blender, post them!"/>
